  "excerpt": "A note.",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"/>\n\t<title></title>\n\t<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"LibreOffice 7.0.4.2 (Linux)\"/>\n\t<meta name=\"created\" content=\"2021-03-05T16:42:28.120807218\"/>\n\t<meta name=\"changed\" content=\"2021-03-05T17:35:08.882985517\"/>\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t@page { size: 21cm 29.7cm; margin: 2cm }\n\t\tp { margin-bottom: 0.25cm; line-height: 115%; background: transparent }\n\t\ta:link { color: #000080; so-language: zxx; text-decoration: underline }\n\t\ta:visited { color: #800000; so-language: zxx; text-decoration: underline }\n\t</style>\n</head>\n<body lang=\"en-US\" link=\"#000080\" vlink=\"#800000\" dir=\"ltr\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">\nSuicide note:</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\"><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">\tI am fed up with\nlife full of loneliness, slander, violence, dishonesty, cruelty,\nmental, lack of morality, physical pain, fear, humiliation, and exploitation. After my\nlatest experiments with intoxication I’ve made some foolish\nmistakes that had significant impact on my reputation which I will\nnever be able to fix. Therefore I decided to take away my own life.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">\t</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">Yours:</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">Mirosław Zbigniew\nLeśniak</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">aka wsky/wintersky</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\"><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\">PS: I prefer\ncremation.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\"><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%\"><br/>\n</p>\n<img src=\"/assets/images/me.jpeg\">\n</body>\n</html>\n",
